::Zardus/Prowl::

As Zardus stumbles forward as Ramhorn's shots hit him, Prowl launches himself 
into the air, swooping down to Iron Raptor and grabbing her in his talons. He 
flies off toward the roof of the Ark, taking the shots that were meant for 
her.

"Slag!" Zardus swears, getting up and looking up at where Ramhorn was. He 
fires several shots at him before flying off in pursuit of Prowl.
